<p><span><strong>什么是治愈系？</strong></span></p>
<p><strong><span>就是我见过这世间的丑陋之后，</span></strong></p>
<p><strong><span>依然选择，</span></strong></p>
<p><strong><span>温柔待你！</span></strong></p>
